Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ox. Box. Fox.[Sofia在学习]\NOx. Box. Fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bullock先生 －早上好\N-Mr Bullock. -Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 Sofia 很抱歉 打扰你学习了\NMorning, Sofia. Sorry to interrupt your lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,－我们结束了 －很抱歉 索菲亚  我们还没结束\N-We're finished.-No, we're not, Sofia...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下楼继续学习\Nand we'll continue downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,矿山被分给了三个郡\NHills get divided into three counties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,每个郡都有一个特派员\NEach county has a commissioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,－由谁来认命？ －州长\N-Appointed by fucking who? -The governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,－什么时候任命？ －已经任命了\N-When the fuck does that happen? -lt already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,－有我认识的人么 －是从杨克顿直接下派的\N-Anyone I know? -They're all from Yankton.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well 作为信使 尽管带来的是个坏消息\NWell, being as you're the bearer of unsettling news...
