Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没有矿区的人，huh？\NNo one from the fucking hills, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,都是Pennington的人\NAll Pennington's people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,省点功夫吧\NSaves time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用不用找个地方 杀了他们\NJust travel to one destination,murder the three of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看他们死了怎么当物派员\Nsee how they like being commissioner after they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,马车到了 Lila\NCoach coming, Lila.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,－你的朋友和姑娘们 也一起来了？ －我不清楚\N-With your friend and her girls? -I don't know.
