Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,－你想让我和你一起去看看？ －Oh 不 不\N-You want me to come watch with you? -Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well 好吧\NWell, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well 你忙你的 我在外面等你\NWell, do whatever you want, but I'll wait outside for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些收据 除了Hendy lron的这张\NAll the invoices other than this mission from Hendy lron
