Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你签个字 然后我先付清一部分\NYou'll note I've made partial payment to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NYes.
