Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你上次接到陌生人的来信是他妈的什么时候的事了？\NWhen's the last time you got a fucking letter from a stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,－我爸爸去世 －去世？\N-Bad news about Pa. -Bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,损害我们的利益的企图就是我们和陌生人的唯一的沟通方式\NTries against our interests is our sole communications from strangers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以无论如何 我们得到处立电线杆\Nso by all means, let's plant poles all across the country...
