Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他都不屑于我的想法 huh？\Nand blinker our judgements of motive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你比我想的还多\NYou've given it more thought than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,事情现在还不够糟么？\NAin't the state of things cloudy enough?
