Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要刀\NI won't need no fucking knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从阳台掉下来了\NThey went over the fucking balcony!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸的是\NAwful possibility in these matters...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,两个人都会很疼\Nis both men sustaining mortal injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你找死 混蛋\NYou looking to die, cocksucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,－你不能杀他 －该死的\N-He ain't your kill! -God damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey 别再往前走了\NHey, hey. Hey, don't come no further!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\NJesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:21:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\NJesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,万能的上帝啊\NJesus Christ almighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,－Bullock在哪呢 －我擦\N-Where's Bullock? -Fuck me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我有刀\NI do have a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,现在刀在我手上\NIt come to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到朽木镇\NWelcome to fucking Deadwood!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿很好战的\NIt can be combative.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我还真是少有的幸运啊\NBut I'm rarely that fucking lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,扔个便士在犹太人鼻子上吧(指的是邮局老头查理斯)\NWave a penny under the Jew's nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他还活着(子弹擦着耳边飞过)\NThey got living breath in them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:22:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,老天眷顾他(应该叫做幸运便士？)\Nit brings them right around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullock先生\NMr Bullock.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,－真是惊喜－没人死亡\N-A happy surprise. -No one's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.64,0:23:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Star先生的肩受伤了\NMr Star's shoulder's been hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是你们的高档妓女朋友Maddie么？\NAin't that your high-end whore friend Maddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得她不是把家当搬到了纽约么？\NThat I thought had took her snatch to New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 人们开始闲逛了\NWonderful how folks can get around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.64,0:23:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,医生Cochran需要从Whitewood镇赶回来么？\NDoc Cochran needs to come from Whitewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A.W. Merrick.\NA.W. Merrick.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Star和Utter先生先扶到我们的店里吧\NMr Star and Utter should be taken to our store.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 Bullock先生\NHello, Mr Bullock.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.64,0:23:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  William\NHello, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好\NI’m all right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.60,0:23:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我会很感激你们\NI'd be grateful...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果帮忙把她们的行李搬到屋子里\Nif you'd take their belongings to a house...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在西边建的那所\NI built on the west edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.96,0:24:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来给Maddie看座吧 Joanie.\NBetter let me hold Maddie's chair, Joanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.88,0:24:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我得给人家一个好的印象\NI need to make a fucking impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.80,0:24:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,－女士 －大人\N-My lady. -My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.64,0:24:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我对我的疏忽很抱歉\NLack of notice is my only regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.44,0:24:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的错 没先告诉Joanie\NThat's my fault for giving Joanie none.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.08,0:24:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你做好最坏打算了么 Maddie\NWere you hedging your bets, Maddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.52,0:24:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,来这个营地我早已无所畏惧了\NFeared losing my nerve all the way to the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.56,0:24:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道的是 马车不是把你带到了葛底士堡么 huh?\NThen wondered, had that coach brought you to Gettysburg, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,葛底士堡 战场\NGettysburg, fucking battle carnage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.60,0:24:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,－是的 我听着呢 －什么？\N-Yes, I wondered. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,津津有味\NWondered.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.04,0:24:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你买下了那所房子 甜心 什么时候的事？\NYou secured that building, honey, when?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.16,0:24:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,11月\NNovember.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.36,0:24:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,11月拿到了那所房子？\NGot the building in November...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.20,0:25:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你会在那之后找到\NI guess you'll be operating out of?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.16,0:25:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我本以为这就是个闹剧 过后就忘了 因为Joanie的钱\NI'd have thought a trick would have been behind it, but Joanie's fuck money...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.60,0:25:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,已经花在了珠宝上\Nhas been going for jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.92,0:25:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们互相了解已经多长时间了 甜心？\NHow long we had that understanding, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.64,0:25:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,从我14岁开始\NSince I was 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.40,0:25:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我给她珠宝\NI've been giving Joanie jewels...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.80,0:25:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,作为她的嫖资 从她14岁开始\Nfor her fuck money since she was 14 years of age...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.32,0:25:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不止一次我站出来保护她\Nand not once did I come out ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.68,0:25:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何\NAnyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.80,0:25:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何\NAnyways....
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.16,0:25:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,从11月开始\NSince November...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.64,0:25:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉这事要不了了之了 但我猜\Nit looked to me the project lay fallow, but I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.08,0:25:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,它那时刚刚开始吧\Nit was just germinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.76,0:25:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们能私下谈谈么 Cy？-那会显得失礼么？\N-Shall we talk in private, Cy? -Would that be rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.56,0:25:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也不\NNot at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.64,0:25:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 我和Joanie18年的交情了\NI mean, a 18-year relationship between me and Joanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.72,0:25:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你能离开一下么\Nand just one moment alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.52,0:25:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以\NOf course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.32,0:25:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意 也可以顺便做点生意\NSuck some pricks if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.16,0:25:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嫖资你都留着把 就当是我给你的礼物了\NKeep whatever they give you as my way of saying welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.76,0:25:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这会有不开眼的看上我么？\NAny blind ones out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.08,0:25:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\NJesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.64,0:25:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-绷带得缠紧点 AI -缠吧\N-That bandage wants to be tight, Al. -That does it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.24,0:25:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你把它缠自己脖子上试试 [太他妈紧了]\NAsk it if it wants to be wound around your fucking neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.56,0:25:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,离我远点 Barney\NGet away from me, Barney!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.00,0:25:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.84,0:26:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,欠干的Adams\NFucking Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.64,0:26:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他制止了你  不是么？\NRestrained you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.20,0:26:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在大道上他阻止了我 现在他又想找个小妞了\NObstructs me in the thoroughfare. Now he wants to bill and coo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.24,0:26:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,擦\NFuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.28,0:26:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那个犹太人是怎么想的呢 Dan 想拿手枪扑过来？\NWhat was that Jewish fellow thinking, Dan, to charge at me with a purse gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.80,0:26:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这事我也不常见\NThis is an unfamiliar situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.24,0:26:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是有点过于想证明自己了\NHe just overplayed trying to prove himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.12,0:26:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,总之整件事是因什么而起呢？\NWhat was that whole damn thing about anyhow?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.56,0:26:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,AI想把Bullock拉过来\NAl's calling Bullock to the fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.84,0:26:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullock也不是AI一路的啊\NBullock ain't even of Al's flock.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.24,0:26:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,AI现在想招点人 但不当做心腹\NAl's gonna be calling numbers to the fold now that he can't trust like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.20,0:26:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是他不喜欢的人\NSome he don't even like.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.20,0:26:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要并入美国了\NWe're joining America.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.00,0:26:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,满嘴谎言 你不能信那帮混蛋\NAnd it's full of lying, thieving cocksuckers that you can't trust at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.56,0:26:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,州长 特派员 以及其他类似的\NGovernors, commissioners, whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.92,0:26:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,以上帝的名义 那有点难以接受\NBy God, that's just the new way of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.72,0:26:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要习惯就行了 Jonhnny\NAnd you just gonna have to get used to it, Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.60,0:26:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-好吧 -你不能不接受\N-All right. -You gonna have to accept it...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.80,0:26:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,并学会控制住自己\Nand learn to control yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.16,0:27:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必和我争论了\NYou get no argument from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.76,0:27:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.12,0:27:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是我逼你的 小姐\NIt's been me nudging you from the nest, young lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.36,0:27:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-逼你飞走的 -好吧\N-urging you to take fucking wing. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.84,0:27:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪得来的钱买那个地方\NWhere did the money come from that bought that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.68,0:27:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸以6.5美元的价格把你卖给了我\NYour daddy sold me you for $6.50...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.08,0:27:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,而有个有钱的亲戚也很难瞒住我的\Nso a rich relation is tough to swallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.96,0:27:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别对我撒谎就是对我的尊重 honey\NIt is respectful not to lie, honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.48,0:27:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是要是继续沉默就别怪我不客气\Nbut any further silence will get me violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.32,0:27:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道钱是哪来的\NYou know where that backing came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.40,0:27:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eddie Sawyer的临别赠礼？\NA farewell gesture from Eddie Sawyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.08,0:27:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道Eddie从我这偷钱[Eddie负责赌博]\NI knew Eddie had been stealing from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.64,0:27:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,后来他跑了 同时你突然买了那个地方\Nand then he flees and you turn up owning that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.52,0:27:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再在这工作了 Cy 你明白么？\NI don't work here no more, Cy. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.08,0:27:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么？\NNo matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.36,0:27:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了你或者放你走\NIt's kill you or let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.36,0:27:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我能忍心让你死么？\NCould I make it with you dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.16,0:28:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要试呢？\NWhy try?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.52,0:28:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看看\NLook at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.68,0:28:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这动人的微笑\NLook at that beautiful smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.12,0:28:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 亲爱的\NAll right, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.04,0:28:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让我\NLet me...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.04,0:28:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,让你走吧\NIet you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.08,0:28:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.20,0:28:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要不要\NShall we....
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.32,0:28:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出去一下 当Maddie\NI'll take the air while Maddie...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.60,0:28:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,听到这个好消息的时候\Nhears the happy news.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.56,0:28:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们去找那个老太婆\NLet's go get the fucking crone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.32,0:28:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉自己是个孩子 我想蹦起来\NI feel like a boy. I feel like skipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.48,0:28:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我祝福你 鼓励你\NI'm that fucking hopeful and excited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.68,0:28:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,热水\NHot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.72,0:29:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉吴\NTell Wu...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.80,0:29:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,最好别用酒鬼喂猪\Nthat that drunk better not get ate by his pigs...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.84,0:29:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我找到办法处理尸体\Nuntil I have had my way with the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.68,0:29:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我做好准备了 医生 如果你想开始挖子弹的话\NI'm braced, Doc, if you want to start digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.56,0:29:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,马上\NMomentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.00,0:29:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 夫人 耳鸣\NThank you, ma'am. The ringing....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.24,0:29:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好 William\NI'm all right, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.96,0:29:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你的枪和徽章哪儿去了 Bullock先生？\NWhere are your gun and badge, Mr Bullock?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.68,0:29:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我和那个和我打架的人是私人恩怨\NIt was personal between me and the man I fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.12,0:29:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我摘下了\Nso I took them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.84,0:29:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但他有刀啊\NBut he kept a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.68,0:29:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我卸掉武器的时候并不知道\NI didn't know that when I disarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.28,0:29:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那你现在要因为那把刀逮捕他么？\NWill you arrest him now for the knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.20,0:29:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你问的够多了 William\NThat's questions enough for Mr Bullock, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.72,0:29:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,给他点鸦片酒\NGive him a little dose of that laudanum.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.96,0:29:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我受得了 医生\NI got my load on, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.48,0:30:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,毋庸置疑\NDon't doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.76,0:30:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我会拿回我的枪和徽章\NI'll have back my gun and badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.44,0:30:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,擦\NFuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.08,0:30:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我留意到了这些东西在你的夜壶里 知道这不是你的\NI found these seeing to your piss-pot, and I know they ain't yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.04,0:30:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,什么告诉你的 那个该死的徽章？\NWhat tipped you off, the fucking badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.72,0:30:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,放下\NPut them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.40,0:30:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,值得背后高兴么\NIs that some kind of private fucking hilarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.60,0:30:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么？-观察我的夜壶\N-What? -The piss-pot remark.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.32,0:30:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.76,0:30:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,早上我把尿\NI made water...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.12,0:30:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,从阳台泼出去了如果这是你该干的事的话\Noff the balcony this morning, if it's any of your fucking business.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.12,0:31:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,现在离我远点\NNow get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.48,0:31:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你 EB 回来\NNot you, E.B. Get the fuck back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.80,0:31:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老天啊\NHeavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.80,0:31:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就像发生了史诗般的战斗\NIt's all like some great Greek battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.76,0:31:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah 医生呢 Huh？\NYeah, how about that fucking Doc, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.80,0:31:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,去诊治道貌岸然的人\NSeeing to the respectable types...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.60,0:31:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,却扔下我们 这些定期的主顾 huh？\NIeaving us, the ones that pay him regular, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.96,0:31:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 那个女的和孩子\NSo, that woman and child...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.88,0:31:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是Bullock的？\NBullock's?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.96,0:31:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他的妻子和儿子\NHis wife and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.80,0:31:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Star先生 Charlie Utter都怎么样了\NHow was Mr Star? How was Charlie Utter?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.64,0:31:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 Johnny\NShut up, Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.24,0:31:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,查清Bullock被打成什么样了\NDetail Bullock's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.80,0:31:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服坏了 视线模糊\NThe worse for wear. No clarity to his look or focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.16,0:31:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,当我查看其他参与者的时候\Nas I could cite in other combatants.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.28,0:31:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你碰我了 EB\NYou touch me, E.B...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.12,0:31:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我他妈要把你鼻子穿过你脑袋\NI'll put your nose through your fucking brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.88,0:31:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,NOW 他说他下一步的打算了么\NNow, did he state his further intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.64,0:31:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拿回枪和徽章\NTo have his gun and badge back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.76,0:31:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,用什么语气\NIn what fucking tone?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.92,0:31:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.12,0:31:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,直呼你的名字让我受宠若惊 AI 他当时在对一个8岁孩子讲话\NI'd shy from putting a name on it, Al. He was talking to an 8-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.00,0:31:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,听上去就像他会回来要求更多一样？\NSound like he'd be coming back for more?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.52,0:32:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well 我不想猜 以免猜错\NWell, I'd hate to guess and be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.36,0:32:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,马车上有新的妓女 huh？\NNew whores on that coach, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.48,0:32:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,查清他们在哪工作\NFind out where they'll be working.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.04,0:32:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以把东西带给他 顺便探探他的底\NI could take him his gun and badge, plumb his intent as we talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.88,0:32:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那你们的谈话要怎么开始呢 huh？\NAnd how would that chat start, E.B., huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.92,0:32:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‘这是你的东西 而他看起来就像个逼一样’\N"Here's your hardware, and as he looks a cunt anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.60,0:32:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‘无论如何AI想让你接受胜利者的荣誉’\N"Al would like you to have this rose."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.00,0:32:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我去调查一下新的妓女\NI'll look into the new whores.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.88,0:32:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你要怎么处理\NHow you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.28,0:32:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,子弹取出来了么？Star先生还活着？\NIs my bullet out? Will Star live?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.16,0:32:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,－如果他死了 他会高兴一些 －Utter先生呢？\N-lf he don't, he's going happy. -And Mr Utter?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.92,0:32:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,－他会瞎了或者聋了么？－不会的\N-Will he be blind and deaf? -No!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.16,0:32:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我得弄点新的情报 在我又被责难之前\NLet me suss out that new trim, Johnny, before I earn some added rebuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.24,0:32:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,看 正如我说的那样 我不是你们的敌人\NLook, all's I'm saying is, I ain't your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.44,0:33:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你怎么想 如果我认为你做得事十次有九次是有敌意的\NWhatever you thought your intentions was coming on me like you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.48,0:33:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那第十次就会是你这辈子的最后一次行动\Nnine times out of ten, that'll be the last fucking move you ever make.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.56,0:33:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullock会回来拿武器\NBullock will be coming back for his weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.32,0:33:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,－出于什么目的？－涵待解决的问题\N-To what intent? -Open question.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.32,0:33:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well 我们会做好准备的\NWell, we'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.08,0:33:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你开始你的第一次了\NYou've had your one out of 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.76,0:33:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子瞪着眼睛向马车外看 我就那么娘么？\NCow-eyed kid looking from that coach, that's what fucking unmanned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.28,0:33:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他应该不知道她要来的\NHe couldn't have known she was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.52,0:33:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就在今天 我询问Bullock他家庭的情况\NJust today, I'd asked Mr Bullock after his family and...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.04,0:33:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他没提她们已经在路上了\Nhe made no mention of their being en route.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.76,0:33:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well 您真好 还搭把手\NWell, you're kind, extending the hand of welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.68,0:33:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well 最好这个营地能禁止外来者\NWell, at its best, this camp can be forbidding to new arrivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.24,0:33:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那就有点过了\NThat was very much my experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.12,0:34:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,更不用说一来就看到Bullock先生在道上的泥里打滚\NLet alone to come upon Mr Bullock in the mud of that thoroughfare...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.20,0:34:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还受伤了 谁知道会有多严重呢\Ninjured, who knows how seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.64,0:34:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well谢天谢地 他是自己走回去的\NWell, thank goodness, he seemed coming back to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.32,0:34:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,lsringhausen小姐 我没意识到医学\NMiss lsringhausen, I didn't realise medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.24,0:34:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也是你的擅长领域\Nwas among your areas of expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.40,0:34:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是 Garret夫人\NIt isn't, Mrs Garret.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.04,0:34:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我该了解一下Bullock先生的现在情况\NThen perhaps, I'll better learn Mr Bullock's condition in his presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.88,0:34:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,－以及Star'先生和Utter先生的情形 －是的 夫人\N-And Mr Star's and Utter's condition. -Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.44,0:34:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sofia?\NSofia?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.04,0:34:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你把彩带绑在了糖果上？\NYou put a ribbon around your candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.36,0:34:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我把这个送给那个男孩？\NAnd did you want me to give it to that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.48,0:34:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,－请出声回答 Sofia－是的\N-Please answer in words, Sofia. -Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.24,0:34:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,－lsringhausen小姐－Ellsworth先生\N-Miss lsringhausen. -Mr Ellsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.60,0:34:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我来Garret夫人当保镖\NI'm here to steer Mrs Garret.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.20,0:34:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那么Ellsworth和我要一起去送东西\NThen Mr Ellsworth and l will make the delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.68,0:35:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,问个我不该问的 Garret夫人\NNot as I'd been asked, Mrs Garret...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.16,0:35:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但我感觉换一天拜访也许更好\Nbut I wonder if this ain't a call better paid another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.68,0:35:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信我能再找个合适的机会拜访\NI've stopped believing I can dictate the terms of my opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.16,0:35:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well 有人说 不抓住机会\NWell, some would say, it might be your choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.52,0:35:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,也算是一种选择\Nwhat chances you decide not to take...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.68,0:35:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人就是堵不住他的嘴\Nsome being the butt-in loudmouth types.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.96,0:35:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,－我可以一个人走么－不 夫人\N-Shall I walk on alone, Mr Ellsworth? -No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.00,0:35:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思我吐出来了\NI'm sorry for throwing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.24,0:35:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你没有 我就有点怀疑你的以前的习惯了\NIf you hadn't, I'd suspect your previous habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.12,0:35:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,－Bullock先生－Garret夫人\N-Mr Bullock. -Mrs Garret.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.36,0:36:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,－你觉得怎么样 Star先生－我吐了两次\N-How are you feeling, Mr Star? -I've puked twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.44,0:36:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,－Garret.夫人－Trixie\N-Mrs Garret. -Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.20,0:36:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Garret夫人\NMrs Garret.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.68,0:36:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,－Utter先生－夫人\N-Mr Utter? -Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.40,0:36:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不必惊慌 都是旧伤\NDon't be alarmed. A lot of this damage is old.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.52,0:36:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以介绍一下我的妻子Martha和我们的儿子William么？\NMay I introduce my wife Martha and our son William?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.68,0:36:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Alma Garret夫人\NMrs Alma Garret.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.64,0:36:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好 -你好\N-How do you do? -How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.92,0:36:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好 William -你好\N-How do you do, William? -How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.52,0:36:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是Ellsworth Garret夫人事务的执行总裁\NAnd Ellsworth, who superintends Mrs Garret's claim
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.84,0:36:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-夫人 William -你好\N-Madam. William. -How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.36,0:36:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能发现我们现在处境不妙\NYou've discovered us in distressing circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.56,0:36:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很安全 而且也很高兴联系上了Bullock先生\NWe're safe and glad of joining Mr Bullock.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.16,0:36:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望这些对你们能有点用处\NI hope this can be of some use to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.16,0:36:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-对你们安家 -谢谢\N-in your settling in. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.96,0:37:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.28,0:37:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子给你儿子的礼物也在里面\NMy ward includes sweets for your son...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.24,0:37:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他妈妈允许他接受的话\Nwhen his mother decides he may have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.32,0:37:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-你孩子是个男孩？ -是个女孩 叫Sofia\N-ls your ward a boy? -A girl, Sofia.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.88,0:37:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-比你小点 我感觉 -Oh\N-A little younger than you, I think. -Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.24,0:37:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.48,0:37:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你想起我信里提过Garret夫人吧\NYou recall Mrs Garret from my letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.28,0:37:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.64,0:37:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你能拿到信真是好运\NThat's good luck you had right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.24,0:37:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是送信的。但我得今天得承认我一直很外行\NBecause I carry the mail, and I'll admit today before laypeople...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.08,0:37:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,弄丢的比我送到的要多\Nwe lose more letters than we deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.92,0:37:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就走了啊！希望很快能再次见到你\NI'll say good-bye then, in hopes that I see you again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.24,0:38:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.04,0:38:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-希望也能见到你 William -谢谢你的好意\N-I hope I see you soon, William. -Thanks for the sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.52,0:38:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可以来找我问那些好的钓鱼地点哦\NAnd don't be pestering me for the good fishing spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.20,0:38:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我在中央旅馆吃早饭时候才给它们起得名字\NI name them only over breakfast at the Grand Central Hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.64,0:38:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是我叫狗的时候\Nor, when I call my dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.88,0:38:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-你想看下你房子么？-我很想\N-Will you see your house? -I would like to very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.24,0:38:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullock夫人 我从你之前的东西里取回了你的帽子\NMrs Bullock, I've retrieved your bonnet from your former post...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.24,0:38:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在你方便的时候\Nand at your convenience...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.88,0:38:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,黑山先锋报的读者很想听听\Nthe readers of the Black Hills Pioneer would be interested in...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.68,0:38:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,您的旅途趣闻 可能的话还有您的对营地的第一印象\Nhearing about your journey and perhaps, your first impressions of our camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.72,0:38:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必全都回答他们\NYou don't have to give them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.88,0:38:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢你 请照看Star先生-好的。不用急着回来\N-Thank you for seeing to Mr Star. -No need to hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.64,0:38:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧！William\NGo ahead, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.16,0:38:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你写给他老婆的信里都没提我 是不？\NHe never wrote of me in his letters to her, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.00,0:39:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Garret夫人 我们也没谈他在信里写了什么或者没写什么啊\NWe never spoke on what he's wrote to his wife or hadn't, Mrs Garret.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.20,0:39:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,或者 他为什么没写\NOr why he hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.16,0:39:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\NNo, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.72,0:39:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们俩也不应该谈这个\NAnd you and me hadn't ought to, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.00,0:39:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你陪我过来 Ellsworth先生\NThank you for taking me, Mr Ellsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.68,0:39:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气 夫人\NYou're welcome, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.76,0:39:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你想起\NYou'll recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.60,0:39:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我信里关于他丈夫的事了么？\Nwhat I wrote about her husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.08,0:39:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么要回买矿山的钱的\NHow he'd sought his money back on a claim?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.96,0:39:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,摔死了\NHe died in a fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.80,0:39:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在获赔之前 却发现那是个富矿\Nbefore gaining satisfaction, and the claim proved out rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.84,0:39:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是那所房子么？ 前面那所很漂亮的\NIs that the house, sir, the splendid one ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.52,0:39:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.64,0:39:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以先走一步 William\NYou can walk ahead a little piece, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.64,0:39:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但不能走远\NJust a little piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.64,0:40:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,出于承诺 我得帮这个寡妇一把\NAnd, of my promise to help the widow...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.52,0:40:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,尽我所能\Nas I could...
